Package: TranscripTools
Title: Streamlined RNA-seq Data Manipulation and Analysis
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Francesco Edoardo Vallone", email = "francesco.edo.vallone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: TranscripTools provides lightweight helper functions for bulk RNA-seq workflows,
 built to speed up analyses that involve multiple differential expression
 comparisons. It includes utilities to filter and annotate DE results, generate
 common plots (volcano, heatmap, PCA), run enrichment analysis wrappers, and
 export nested results to analysis-ready tables for reporting.
